                        <p><span><b>Solved Problem: </b></span>Express 5% w/w as a ratio strength.</p>
                        <p><span><b>Approach: </b></span>convert the percentage strength to a ratio and simplify.</p>
                    <div class="formulae"><p>$$ {5 \% \over 100 \%} = {1 \ part \over x \ parts}$$</p></div>
                        <p><span><b>Answer: </b></span>1 : 20</p>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                
                
                
                <tr>
