                        <p><span><b>Solved Problem: </b></span>Express 1:200 as a percentage strength.</p>
                        <p><span><b>Approach: </b></span>Set up a ratio from the ratio strength to a percentage.</p>
                    <div class="formulae"><p>$$ {1 \ part \over 200 \ parts} = {x \%  \over 100 \%}$$</p></div>
                        <p><span><b>Answer: </b></span> 0.5% </p>
                    </td>
